WEBVTT

1
00:33:01.420 --> 00:33:03.350 
你不是说为她高兴吗
You said that you were happy for her.

2
00:33:03.390 --> 00:33:05.620 
说过很多回呢
You said that a lot of times.

3
00:33:05.650 --> 00:33:07.090 
是的 我是真的替她开心
I am. I am happy for her.

4
00:33:07.120 --> 00:33:10.360 
我绝对不会破坏她的幸福
I would never do anything to take that away from her.

5
00:33:10.390 --> 00:33:12.930 
我只是...
I am,uh...

6
00:33:14.460 --> 00:33:15.960 
...感到悲伤
...grieving.

7
00:33:18.500 --> 00:33:23.100 
我为我俩失去的...
Uh,I'm grieving what we both lost...

8
00:33:24.470 --> 00:33:25.570 
为我女儿失去的...
...and what my daughter lost

9
00:33:25.610 --> 00:33:28.580 
为阴差阳错而悲伤
for the bad timing.

10
00:33:28.610 --> 00:33:31.750 
而且 我爱你
And I love you.

